Address Book

For information about the HOUSE OF COMMONS

House of Commons Information Office

House of Commons

London SW1A 2TT

Tel: 020 7219 4272

Fax: 020 7219 5839

Email: hcinfo@parliament.uk

(Please note that messages for MPs cannot be accepted)

Recorded Business Statement: Tel: 020 7219 5532

Hours: Monday – Thursday 9 am – 6 pm, Friday 9 am – 4.30 pm. (During recess 10 am – 5 pm every day).

Information available on the Internet: http://www.parliament.uk/

The Weekly Information Bulletin is published on the internet at 12.30 pm on the Monday following publication. It can be found by following links from Parliament’s home page.
